Event staff scan registrations and hand out lanyards at the entrance. Consulting firms stack glossy case study booklets on high tables, and small groups analyze which recruiters seem most enthusiastic. Finance firms offer QR codes for immediate internship applications, and the engineering society sponsors a resume review table near the stage. A whiteboard lists employers scheduling same-day interviews, and a post-event survey link flashes on the monitors near the exit. Recruiters also remind students to follow up with personalized emails. Additionally, a cybersecurity company runs a password cracking challenge on a laptop. Announcement chimes signal the final hour of the fair.

An aroma of coffee and catered snacks spreads from the lounge as students exit with tote bags filled with branded notebooks, pens, and a stack of business cards distributed by recruiters. A welcome announcement outlining the fair schedule is being broadcast over the PA system. Meanwhile, a cybersecurity company runs a password cracking challenge on a laptop, a data science company showcases a live dashboard of fair attendance, and a robotics startup flies a small drone above its booth to attract attention. Announcement chimes signal the final hour of the fair. Some students rehearse elevator pitches quietly against the wall, and after the event, friends decompress on the quad, comparing which companies responded warmly.

Groups of friends mark target employers on the event map, and a whiteboard lists employers scheduling same-day interviews, with interview sign-up sheets filling with names and a post-event survey link flashing on the monitors near the exit.
